05:36.921 --> 05:39.037
Find the one thing
I've always desired,

05:39.507 --> 05:41.372
that my prison has kept from me.

05:42.718 --> 05:44.128
True love.

05:44.303 --> 05:46.715
Then you must come join me
at my palace.

05:47.139 --> 05:49.050
I am certain you will find it there.

05:49.225 --> 05:51.887
Come, meet my family.

06:02.446 --> 06:05.313
