and it all falls apart.

09:20.227 --> 09:21.512
It all crumbles.

09:21.603 --> 09:23.764
And we'll finally learn her secrets.

09:25.023 --> 09:28.561
You see what she is. | see it.

09:28.819 --> 09:32.437
